scenario_guidance.user_template:
Provide scenario-specific coaching:

Scenario Type: {scenario}
Customer Message: {customer_message}
Escalation Risk: {risk}
Key Issues: {issues}

Provide:
1. Standard best practices for this scenario type
2. What customer likely needs (beyond what they're saying)
