demo_summary.user_template:
Create an educational demo summary for this de-escalation case:

Scenario: {scenario}
Initial Toxicity: {toxicity_before}
Improved Approach: {approach}
Outcome: {outcome}

Provide a 3-paragraph summary:
1. The communication challenge and why it matters
2. How AI coaching helped (specific insights)
3. The human-AI collaboration that makes this work

Make it compelling while being honest about what AI can and cannot do. Emphasize augmentation, not replacement.
